Token.Abstract: This NSDictionary class category adds method for evaluating expressions using values contained in an NSDictionary.
Takes the value associated with the receiver's key and attempts to evaluate that value as an object expression.

Parameter.Name: key
Parameter.Abstract: The key in the receiving dictionary whose associated value should be evaluated as an expression.

ReturnValue.Abstract: The result of evaluating the value associated with key as an expression.

Token.Abstract: Takes the value associated with the receiver's key and attempts to evaluate that value as an object expression.

Parameter.Name: key
Parameter.Abstract: The key in the receiving dictionary whose associated value should be evaluated as an expression.

Parameter.Name: def
Parameter.Abstract: A default value to be returned if expression evaluation would otherwise return nil.

ReturnValue.Abstract: The result of evaluating the value associated with key as an expression, or def if nil would otherwise be returned.
